title: Dream Bigger
itunes:title: Dream Bigger
description:
Episode 136 - We're all thinking too small. We need to take all of your goals and dreams and 10x them. In this episode I talk about about how we need to learn not to fear dreaming big, we need to fear being small. I made this episode as a wake up call you can listen to every morning.
